OL,3,CFormer Post Office boss says he's
OL,4,C'subject of a smear campaign' by
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FMr Staunton once again denied he had
OL,8,Flied about being told to stall on
OL,9,Fcompensation payments, and said he has
OL,10,F"spoken up on genuine matters of
OL,11,Fpublic concern".
OL,13,FBy Maya Bowles, ITV Westminster
OL,14,FProducer
OL,16,FFormer Post Office chair Henry
OL,17,FStaunton has told MPs on the business
OL,18,Fand trade select committee he's been
OL,19,Fthe victim of "a smear campaign" by
OL,20,Fthe government for "standing up for"
OL,21,Fsub-postmasters.
