OL,7,FMy Staunton, when she called him a
OL,8,Fliar for saying he had been told to
OL,9,Fdelay compensation payments by a
OL,10,Fsenior civil servant.
OL,12,FMPs have been quizzing the current and
OL,13,Fformer Post Office bosses, along with
OL,14,Fformer sub-postmaster Alan Bates,
OL,15,Fabout the Horizon scandal and progress
OL,16,Fon compensation.
OL,18,FPressure has been mounting on the
OL,19,Fgovernment and the Post Office to
OL,20,Ffully compensate sub-postmasters since
OL,21,Fthe airing of ITV drama in January.
