OL,3,CFormer Post Office boss says he's
OL,4,C'subject of a smear campaign' by
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FMore than 700 branch managers were
OL,8,Fprosecuted by the Post Office between
OL,9,F1999 and 2015 after faulty Horizon
OL,10,Faccounting software made it look as
OL,11,Fthough money was missing from their
OL,12,Fshops.
OL,14,FHenry Staunton
OL,16,FHenry Staunton was the chair of the
OL,17,FPost Office from December 2022, until
OL,18,Fhe was sacked by business secretary
OL,19,FKemi Badenoch last month.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/14
