OL,3,CFormer Post Office boss says he's
OL,4,C'subject of a smear campaign' by
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,F"What I have done is stand up the
OL,8,Fpostmasters", he said.
OL,10,FIn a statement he read out, Mr
OL,11,FStaunton said he's been the victim of
OL,12,Fa "smear campaign" by the government
OL,13,Fbecause he's "spoken up on matters of
OL,14,Fgenuine public concern".
OL,16,FMs Badenoch is currently at a
OL,17,Fconference in Abu Dhabi, but issued a
OL,18,Fletter to the chair of the business
OL,19,Fcommittee Liam Byrne in which she
OL,20,Fdoubles down on her position against
OL,21,FMr Staunton.
