OL,4,C'subject of a smear campaign' by
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,F"Sunlight is the best disinfectant",
OL,8,Fshe says, before laying out a number
OL,9,Fof rebuttals against Mr Staunton's
OL,10,Fclaims.
OL,12,FMs Badenoch also said the former Post
OL,13,FOffice chair was being investigated
OL,14,Fover "bullying allegations" before his
OL,15,Fdismissal.
OL,17,FFormer sub-postmaster Alan Bates whose
OL,18,Fstory was at the centre of the ITV
OL,19,Fdrama is giving evidence on Monday
OL,20,Falongside former sub-postmasters Tony
OL,21,FDowney and Tim Brentnall.
