OL,3,CFormer Post Office boss says he's
OL,4,C'subject of a smear campaign' by
OL,5,Cgovernment
OL,7,FMr Bates urged the Post Office to just
OL,8,F"get on and pay people" in his
OL,9,Fevidence to MPs on the committee.
OL,11,F"It's not about words, it's about
OL,12,Fdeeds", he said.
OL,14,FThe former sub-postmaster told MPs he
OL,15,Fwas unhappy with the speed of
OL,16,Fcompensation.
OL,18,FWhen asked if the redress was getting
OL,19,Ffaster and fairer, Mr Bates said
OL,20,F"speaking personally of my claim, I
OL,21,Fcan say no, it isn't."
