OL,7,FEarlier this month Mr Bates which he
OL,8,Fsaid was around a sixth of what he
OL,9,Fasked for.
OL,11,FMr Bates also said the Post Office was
OL,12,F"a dead duck" and should be "sold to
OL,13,FAmazon for #1".
OL,15,FNick Read is the current CEO of the
OL,16,FPost Office, and has been since 2019.
OL,18,FLiam Byrne MP, the chair of the select
OL,19,Fcommittee, asked Mr Read why only "20
OL,20,Fper cent" of the Post Office's budget
OL,21,Ffor redress "has been paid out".
