OL,7,FMr Read told the committee chair he
OL,8,Fhas not had a conversation with the
OL,9,Fbusiness secretary about accelerating
OL,10,Fthe compensation scheme.
OL,12,FWhen asked if he had received written
OL,13,Finstructions from the government to
OL,14,Fspeed up the compensation, Mr Read
OL,15,Fsaid: "I don't think I've got written
OL,16,Finstructions but these are the
OL,17,Fconversations clearly we would have
OL,18,Fwith the department on a regular
OL,19,Fbasis."
