OL,7,FHis comments came after the minister
OL,8,Ffor the Post Office admitted will also
OL,9,Fclear the names of people "who were,
OL,10,Fin fact, guilty of a crime".
OL,12,FConservative MP Jonathan Gullis
OL,13,Freferenced the letter at the committee
OL,14,Fon Tuesday, saying he found it
OL,15,F"extraordinary" that "even under new
OL,16,Fleadership victims are still treated
OL,17,Fwith caution and suspicion, which is
OL,18,Fmaybe not going to lead to other
OL,19,Fcoming forward".
